@Comment:	Daer Uncle David , I hope you feel good. Will I see you soon? love Chi
@Comment:	Chi decides to write to his uncle although he refers to him as the guy in the hospital. Mot dictates the rest of the letter word for word. Spelling <Uncle David> takes a really long time but the letter goes more quickly after that. Bro is extremely distracting by interrupting constantly and criticizing Chi's work
